. Thou shalt make me to hear joy and gladness; the bones that be humbled, they shall rejoice. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af1\afs32 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs26\f1\fs32\insrsid2901317 
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af1\afs32 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs26\f1\fs32\insrsid2049427 Turn Thy face away from my sin
s, and blot out all mine iniquities. Create in me a clean heart, O God, and renew a right spirit within me. Cast me not away from Thy presence, and take not Thy Holy Spirit from me. Restore unto me the joy of Thy salvation, and with Thy governing Spirit e
stablish me. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af1\afs32 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs26\f1\fs32\insrsid2901317 
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af1\afs32 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs26\f1\fs32\insrsid2049427 
